      "body" : "isBiggerThanMaxLong(Long.MAX_VALUE + 1.0) will return false. isBiggerThanMaxLong(Long.MAX_VALUE + 1024.0) will also return false. You get true with doubles &gt;= Long.MAX_VALUE + 1025.0"
