      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "@Samil True. It would return true for any double that is greater than Long.MAX_VALUE, of which there are many. Because of floating point rounding, Long.MAX_VALUE+1.0 is not one of them."
    } ],
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 2009857,
      "reputation" : 26235,
      "user_id" : 1798593,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/be41e365336e709f1bfc2c9866eac8e9?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
      "display_name" : "Patricia Shanahan",
      "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/users/1798593/patricia-shanahan"
    },
