  "link" : "https://stackoverflow.com/questions/16546038/a-long-bigger-than-long-max-value",
  "title" : "A long bigger than Long.MAX_VALUE",
  "body" : "<p>How can I get a long number bigger than Long.MAX_VALUE?</p>\n\n<p>I want this method to return <code>true</code>:</p>\n\n<pre><code>boolean isBiggerThanMaxLong(long val) {\n    return (val &gt; Long.MAX_VALUE);\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
